31
00:02:14,968 --> 00:02:17,436
I want to be a professional,
and I'm gonna be.

32
00:02:17,504 --> 00:02:19,563
I'm just waiting for my invitation.

33
00:02:21,774 --> 00:02:23,298
What's going on here?

34
00:02:23,877 --> 00:02:26,175
-We were just--
-We were just what?

35
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:30,913
You know who this is?
This is Rags, and he's a hustler.

36
00:02:30,984 --> 00:02:34,351
Probably one of the best.
What'd you do? Make him win the first set?

37
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:37,856
-He's up $20.
-He's $20 up. Right, $20 up.

38
00:02:37,991 --> 00:02:40,653
Then you'd be $50 up, then $100,
then you'd be broke.

39
00:02:40,727 --> 00:02:43,093
Come on, Joe, let me play.
I can beat this guy.

40
00:02:43,163 --> 00:02:45,256
Maybe you can and maybe you can't.

41
00:02:45,331 --> 00:02:47,424
But we don't deal with maybes, do we?

42
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:50,526
You don't know all the angles yet,
but I do, all right?

43
00:02:50,603 --> 00:02:53,003
He's bad news.
Even if you win, you can't win.

44
00:02:53,072 --> 00:02:56,530
