I can't win? I don't understand.

45
00:02:56,609 --> 00:02:59,077
You don't have to understand.
Just listen to me.

46
00:02:59,779 --> 00:03:01,474
If the kid wants to play...

47
00:03:01,548 --> 00:03:04,108
why don't you let him play?
He may learn something.

48
00:03:04,184 --> 00:03:07,278
