is how to lose.

49
00:03:07,353 --> 00:03:11,221
I'm trying to do something here.
I'm trying to educate this kid, all right?

50
00:03:11,291 --> 00:03:13,555
So if you got something to say, say it to me.

51
00:03:13,626 --> 00:03:17,062
Otherwise shut the fuck up,
because he's my kid, all right?

52
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,893
He's my fucking kid.

53
00:03:19,732 --> 00:03:23,498
And I'm gonna make him a champion.
So you stay away from him.

54
00:03:33,846 --> 00:03:36,576
-Mail came today, Joe.
-Thanks, Don.

55
00:04:34,073 --> 00:04:36,735
-White boy's got skills.
-No, he can't.

56
00:04:59,699 --> 00:05:00,723
Damn!

57
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,358
Now let me get this straight.

58
00:05:02,435 --> 00:05:05,700
You're saying that
because you and me are friends...

59
00:05:06,005 --> 00:05:07,996
