60
00:05:08,074 --> 00:05:12,135
No, "niggas," all right?
There's a big difference.

61
00:05:12,979 --> 00:05:15,140
That's what I just said. "Nigger."

62
00:05:15,214 --> 00:05:17,580
-No. "Nigga."
-"Nigger."

63
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:19,880
"Nigga," N-l-G-G-A.

64
00:05:23,022 --> 00:05:26,651
