66
00:05:30,797 --> 00:05:34,961
Like that man you're playing, right there?
That's my nigga Charles.

67
00:05:35,468 --> 00:05:37,129
My nigger Charles, right?

68
00:05:37,203 --> 00:05:40,263
Hold it. See, you can't say that.

69
00:05:41,107 --> 00:05:42,904
-Only I can.
-Why?

70
00:05:43,276 --> 00:05:46,302
Because, first of all, you don't say it right.

71
00:05:46,379 --> 00:05:49,314
And second, you don't know Charles. I do.

72
00:05:49,382 --> 00:05:50,747
-You do?
-I do.

73
00:05:50,817 --> 00:05:53,445
