since he was knee-high to a duck.

74
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:56,010
See, me and Charles, nigga, we down.

75
00:05:56,289 --> 00:05:58,086
-You're down?
-Yeah, down.

76
00:05:58,157 --> 00:06:02,218
Of course you're down. You're down
about $5,000. Give me my fucking money.

77
00:06:05,365 --> 00:06:06,764
You know what?

78
00:06:06,966 --> 00:06:10,493
It is absolutely impossible
to have an intelligent conversation...

79
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:12,162
