83
00:06:35,728 --> 00:06:39,789
I mean, you've got them animals in there
eating out of the palm of your hand.

84
00:06:39,866 --> 00:06:44,303
You beat them, you take their money,
you call them names to their faces...

85
00:06:44,370 --> 00:06:45,928
and they love you.

86
00:06:46,005 --> 00:06:47,870
I don't know how you do it.

87
00:06:48,441 --> 00:06:50,272
I never saw anything like it.

88
00:06:50,376 --> 00:06:54,176
Beating a man out of his money, that's easy.
Anybody can do that.

89
00:06:55,081 --> 00:06:57,982
But beating a man out of his money
and making him like it...

90
00:06:58,050 --> 00:06:59,540
that's an art.

91
00:07:00,052 --> 00:07:02,316
That's an art of a true hustler.

92
00:07:03,456 --> 00:07:05,686
But it's getting late...

93
00:07:06,459 --> 00:07:09,553
