to make it happen, right?

192
00:14:59,565 --> 00:15:03,899
You get taken care of, I get taken care of,
and everybody's happy.

193
00:15:04,536 --> 00:15:07,767
And the heaviest thing
you ever have to lift around here...

194
00:15:09,074 --> 00:15:10,598
is a clipboard.

195
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:15,469
Well?

196
00:15:18,117 --> 00:15:21,177
I'm sorry, Bill.
I think you got the wrong guy.

197
00:15:21,253 --> 00:15:24,416
-What?
-Tell Jack I said thanks, okay?

198
00:15:24,623 --> 00:15:26,488
You don't do as I say...

199
00:15:26,558 --> 00:15:30,016
then you and Jack will both
be looking for work somewhere else.

200
00:15:30,095 --> 00:15:32,529
Then you can tell Jack I said we're even.

201
00:15:44,043 --> 00:15:46,238
Johnny, you got a phone call.

202
00:15:51,583 --> 00:15:53,312
Hey, Nick. What's up?

203
00:15:53,719 --> 00:15:54,811
What?

204
00:15:57,923 --> 00:15:59,185
Yeah, I want a game.

205
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:38,953
What I'm saying is that I bet you $200
I can drink both these pints of beer...

206
00:16:39,031 --> 00:16:41,864
-before you drink those shots of Jack.
-Sounds good to me.

207
00:16:41,934 --> 00:16:43,492
That is absolutely impossible.

208
00:16:43,569 --> 00:16:45,901
-Then put up your money.
-No problem.

209
00:16:45,971 --> 00:16:49,566
-Brett, can you spot me?
-Again? You already owe me $200.

210
00:16:49,641 --> 00:16:50,733
I'll pay tomorrow.

211
00:16:50,809 --> 00:16:52,777
No cheating. I know how you guys are.

212
00:16:52,845 --> 00:16:55,336
You can't knock one of my glasses
off the table...

213
00:16:55,414 --> 00:16:57,473
and tell me to lap it up to win my bet.

214
00:16:57,549 --> 00:17:00,848
-Who the fuck do you think we are?
-I know, I just....

215
00:17:01,086 --> 00:17:04,055
