218
00:17:08,227 --> 00:17:09,353
-Deal.
-You're on.

219
00:17:09,428 --> 00:17:11,055
-Fine.
-Sounds good to me.

220
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:12,722
Absolutely. Good luck.

221
00:17:12,798 --> 00:17:15,961
