How much more do I need?

222
00:17:16,402 --> 00:17:18,870
If Tang wins his game,
that should be just enough.

223
00:17:18,937 --> 00:17:21,303
Since when was he satisfied
with just enough?

224
00:17:21,373 --> 00:17:23,568
Tang's right.
Plus I'll need more money for fliers.

225
00:17:23,642 --> 00:17:26,406
You can play Moose a quick game.
He's good for $100.

226
00:17:26,478 --> 00:17:28,844
-Say, Moose!
-Don't mess with me.

227
00:17:28,914 --> 00:17:30,939
