228
00:17:31,016 --> 00:17:34,144
Stupid bitch.
Took her two hours to watch 60 Minutes.

229
00:17:35,421 --> 00:17:37,719
Look, I'm sorry. I made him.... Oh, my God!

230
00:17:38,624 --> 00:17:40,615
-Say, "1, 2, 3, go."
-1, 2, 3, go.

231
00:17:43,929 --> 00:17:46,397
-That hand's quicker.
-What difference does--

232
00:17:46,465 --> 00:17:48,433
-Use your left hand--
-Shut up.

233
00:17:53,338 --> 00:17:56,466
You can't touch my glasses
and I can't touch yours.

234
00:17:56,942 --> 00:17:59,103
It's incredible what's going on.

235
